📖 Example of a Role
Role Name: EC2S3AccessRole

Purpose: Allow an EC2 instance to access an S3 bucket.

Who uses it: The EC2 instance (not a human user).

How: The EC2 instance assumes this role when it runs.

📖 Example of a Policy
Policy Name: S3ReadWritePolicy

Purpose: Define what actions are allowed on the S3 bucket.

Attached to: The EC2S3AccessRole.

